1303.description:
Service: Database | Feature: Transactions | Activity: Concurrent updates

**PROBLEM:** Transactions fail with deadlock. Two transactions lock resources in opposite order. Deadlock detected.

**SYMPTOMS:** Deadlock detected → Transaction 1: locks A then B → Transaction 2: locks B then A → Deadlock

**ROOT CAUSE:** Inconsistent lock order. Transaction 1 locks A then B. Transaction 2 locks B then A. Circular wait.

